<h2 style="padding-top: 0;"><a name="1" id="1"></a>The Wired.com related content spotlighter</h2>
<p>
The Wired.com related content spotlighter is based on the <strong><a
href="http://www.infomous.com" target="_blank">Infomous</a></strong>
interactive text cloud technolgy. This spotlighter shows recent articles from related sections of Wired.com.</p>

<p>Word size indicates how often that word occurse in the articles. Related terms and concepts are linked together with lines.</p>

<p>Click a word to show a list of links to relevant stories on Wired.com. Click
any link to open that article in a new page. </p>

<p>Find out more at <a href="http://www.infomous.com">the Infomous web
site</a></p>

